<title>USA: Intercargo allows Orion to boost stake.</title>
<headline>Intercargo allows Orion to boost stake.</headline>
<dateline>SCHAUMBURG, Ill. 1997-08-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Intercargo Corp said Wednesday it amended an agreement to allow Orion Capital Corp to boost its stake in Intercargo to 35 percent from 25 percent.</p>
<p>Orion, however, will not be allowed to increase its stake even further to 49 percent until June 30, 2000 under terms of the amended agreement, Intercargo said.</p>
<p>Under the previous pact, Orion would have been permitted to boost its ownership to 49 percent after December 30, 1998, and under certain limited circumstances after that date to acquire control of Intercargo.</p>
<p>((-- Reuters Chicago Newsdesk 312-408-8787))</p>
